{"lemma": "عُرْضَةٌ", "slug": "عُرْضَةٌ", "root": "ع.ر.ض", "root_slug": "ع-ر-ض", "root_link": "/words/roots/ع-ر-ض", "pos": "N", "pos_camel": "noun", "paradigm": [], "frequency_in_corpus": 0, "cross_references": {"qac": {"found": true, "lemma_key": "عُرْضَة", "root": "عرض", "pos": "N", "occurrence_count": 1}, "wiktextract": {"found": false}, "lanes": {"found": true, "entry_ids": ["n28693"], "search_url": "https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8F%D8%B1%D9%92%D8%B6%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}}, "translations": {"en": "obstacle, butt", "fa": "مانع، هدف", "ur": "مانع، نشان", "tr": "engel, hedef", "id": "halangan, sasaran", "bn": "বাধা, লক্ষ্য", "es": "obstáculo, blanco", "fr": "obstacle, cible", "de": "Hindernis, Ziel", "ru": "препятствие, цель", "zh": "障碍，靶子"}, "definition": null, "etymology": null, "ipa": null, "lanes_definition": {"source": "lanes", "entries": [{"entry_id": "n28693", "headword_ar": "عُرْضَةٌ", "root": "ErD", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": "is of the measure"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "fuEolapN", "text_ar": "فُعْلَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "in the sense of the measure"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mafoEwlN", "text_ar": "مَفْعولٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", like"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "quboDapN", "text_ar": "قُبْضَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (Bd, ii. 224;) and is applied to"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A thing that is set as an obstacle in the way of a thing:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Bd, TA:) and also to"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a thing that is exposed to a thing:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Bd:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "that is set as a butt, like the butt of archers."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) You say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jaEalotu fulaAnFA EuroDapF lika*aA", "text_ar": "جَعَلْتُ فُلَانًا عُرْضَةً لِكَذَا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", meaning"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "naSabotuhu", "text_ar": "نَصَبْتُهُ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "lahu", "text_ar": "لَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (S, O, K; *) i. e."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I set such a one as an obstacle to such a thing:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "as a butt for such a thing."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "huwa lahu duwnahu EuroDapN", "text_ar": "هُوَ لَهُ دُونَهُ عُرْضَةٌ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He is an obstacle to him intervening in the way of it."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, O.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "fulaAnN EuroDapN liln~aAsi", "text_ar": "فُلَانٌ عُرْضَةٌ لِلنَّاسِ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Such a one is"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a butt to men;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "i. e.]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a person whom men cease not to revile:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, O, Msb, K:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a person to whom men address themselves to do evil, and whom they revile."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Az, TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "humo DuEafaA='u EuroDapN likul~i mutanaAwilK", "text_ar": "هُمْ ضُعَفَا=ءُ عُرْضَةٌ لِكُلِّ مُتَنَاوِلٍ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "They are weak persons; persons who offer themselves as a prey to any one who would take them."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) And it is said in the Kur [ii. 224],"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "walaA tajoEaluwA", "text_ar": "وَلَا تَجْعَلُوا"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A@ll~`hu EuroDapF liA^ayomaAnikumo A^ano tabar~uwA watat~aquwA watuSoliHuwA bayona", "text_ar": "ا@للّٰهُ عُرْضَةً لِاَيْمَانِكُمْ اَنْ تَبَرُّوا وَتَتَّقُوا وَتُصْلِحُوا بَيْنَ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Aln~aAsi", "text_ar": "النَّاسِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, * &c.,) meaning"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "naSobFA", "text_ar": "نَصْبًا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (S, TA;) admitting the two significations of"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "an obstacle"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a butt:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA:) i. e."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "And make not God an obstacle"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "between you and that which may bring you near unto God, &c.: (O, K:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "make not God an obstacle to the performance of your oaths to be pious"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(O, Bd)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "and to fear God and to make reconciliation between men:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "make not God an obstacle, because of your oaths, to your being pious"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.: (Bd:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "make not the swearing by God an obstacle to your being pious"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[&c.]: (Fr:) and Zj says the like of this: (L:) or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EuroDapN", "text_ar": "عُرْضَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "signifies"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "intervention"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "with respect to good and evil; (Abu-l- 'Abbás, O, K;) and the meaning is,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "do not intervene by swearing by God every little while so as not to be pious"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.: (O, K, * TA:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "make not God an object of your oaths, by ordinary and frequent swearing by Him,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Bd,) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a butt for your oaths, like the butt of archers,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in order that ye may be pious"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.; for the habitual swearer emboldens himself against God, and is not pious &c.: (Bd:) or, as some say, the meaning is"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "make not the mention of God a means of strengthening your oaths."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) You say also,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "h`*aA EuroDapN laka", "text_ar": "هٰذَا عُرْضَةٌ لَكَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "as meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "This is a thing prepared for thy common,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "ordinary, use."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(O, TA.) ―         -b2-"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A purpose; an intention;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "an object of desire,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of endeavour;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[as though it were a butt;] syn."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "him~apN", "text_ar": "هِمَّةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (S, O, K.) Hassán says, (S, O,) i. e. Ibn-Thábit, (O, TA,)"}, {"kind": "quote", "text": "waqaAla A@ll~`hu qado yas~arotu junodFA\n                      \n                     \n                        humu AlA^anoSaAru EuroDatuhaA All~iqaA='u"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "And God said I have prepared an army: they are the Ansár; whose purpose,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the object of whose desire, is conflict"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "with the unbelievers]. (S, O, TA. [In one copy of the S, in the place of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "yas~arotu", "text_ar": "يَسَّرْتُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", I find"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aEodadotu", "text_ar": "اَعْدَدْتُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", which signifies the same.]) ―         -b3-"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A pretext; an excuse."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(MA.) ―         -b4-  One says also,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "fulaAnN EuroDapu *aAka", "text_ar": "فُلَانٌ عُرْضَةُ ذَاكَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, O,) or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EuroDapN li*aAka", "text_ar": "عُرْضَةٌ لِذَاكَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, O, K,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Such a one is possessed of the requisite ability and strength for that:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, O, K:) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EuroDapN lil$~ar~i", "text_ar": "عُرْضَةٌ لِلشَّرِّ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "possessed of strength to do evil,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "mischief:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and in like manner"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EuroDapN", "text_ar": "عُرْضَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is applied to two things, and to more. (TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "fulaAnapu EuroDapN lilz~awoji", "text_ar": "فُلَانَةُ عُرْضَةٌ لِلزَّوْجِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, O, K)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Such a female is possessed of sufficient strength for the husband;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[i. e., to be married;] (TA;) or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "liln~ikaAHi", "text_ar": "لِلنِّكَاحِ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "for marriage."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "naAqapN EuroDapN", "text_ar": "نَاقَةٌ عُرْضَةٌ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "liloHijaArapi", "text_ar": "لِلْحِجَارَةِ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A she-camel having strength enough for"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[going upon]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the stones."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, O, K.) And [in like manner]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^asofaArK", "text_ar": "اَسْفَارٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "naAqapN EuroDu", "text_ar": "نَاقَةٌ عُرْضُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A she-camel having strength sufficient for journeys."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, O, K. *) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "h`*aA AlbaEiyri Als~afaru waAlHajaru", "text_ar": "هٰذَا البَعِيرِ السَّفَرُ وَالحَجَرُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EuroDu", "text_ar": "عُرْضُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, O, K)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The strength of this camel is sufficient for journeying and for going over stone."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(IB.)       -A2-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EuroDapN", "text_ar": "عُرْضَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "also signifies"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A kind of trick,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "artifice, in wrestling,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, O, K,) by which one throws down men. (S, O.)"}], "source_refs": ["Bd", "TA", "S", "O", "Msb", "K", "Fr", "L"]}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}